{
  "stem": "24615.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I saw the Russians, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were running, you know, with horses, with some trucks, and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And our neighbor, he asked me if I saw the Germans coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did see did Germans come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I thought maybe they were Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, I didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after the next day, you know, the Germans were there already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we start to go on-- go on back home already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So on the way, you know, my mother went home, and everybody was loading.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, so I was loading too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- they broke-- they broke in in a warehouse, and I got out eggs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got apples.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got some flour, you know, I brought it home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I brought home-- you know what you put on the horses where they pull the wagons-- I brought home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the Germans came in, they occupied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first Germans that-- that came in, they said, Juden, we are not going to bother you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when the next Germans will come in, they're going to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Watch out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're going to bother you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they said it to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they are not going to bother us, but the next Germans, when they will come in, you know, they'll bother us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after the front, you know, the first line went away, like, to Lutsk, you know, whatever, and I think in three or four days, the Germans, they came in, you know, with horses, artillery, with everything.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took me and a neighbor boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we fed horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot what else we did when we were down there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then a German-- another German came over.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
